column19:
Informed consent to participate in research

In this study, we are interested in how people make decisions. If you agree to participate in this study, you will play a decision-making game, as well as answer some brief demographic questions and some questionnaires. The estimated time to complete this study is approximately 15 minutes.  The research is being conducted with the goal of publication in academic journals and presentation at academic conferences.



Risks

Your participation in this study does not involve any physical risk or emotional risk to you beyond the risks of daily life.



Compensation

You will receive the amount specified in the description of the study for your participation. In addition, you may earn a bonus based on your decision in the game, as detailed in the instructions of the study. If you fail the comprehension questions on the instructions, you will not recieve compensation for the study. If you fail any attention checks, you will not recieve compensation for the study.

The bonus will be paid after some delay - once we have collected the responses of all the participants in the study. 



Confidentiality

The data you provide will be collected through a secure online system called Qualtrics and through the Prolific platform. The collected data will be fully anonymized and confidentiality will be maintained. We may report the data in scientific publications and the data may ultimately be stored in online repositories so that other researchers can utilize this information in future research. However, any such data will be completely anonymized and you will not in any way be identifiable from the data stored online or reported in publications.



Contacts

If there is anything about the study or taking part in it that is unclear or that you do not understand, please contact the researcher of this study, through a message in the messaging system.



Subject rights

Participation in this study is voluntary, and you are free to leave the study at any time. If you withdraw at any time, you will receive no monetary compensation.

Do you agree to participate?   Please click below if you agree to participate in the research.

 

Please note: there are a few attention checks throughout the survey. Please pay close attention, and answer carefully. Participants who fail an attention check will not be paid.

column150:
I was advised that the distribution was random, so there was no way to determine which were one shape over another. I did find that I did not want to pick a location that was close to the location already picked by the other player. It was almost as if in my mind being further away would be "more random" than a closer location. 
In addition, I see that there were questions about compulsive gambling in the survey. I am a compulsive gambler who has been in therapy for this for several years. I have not gambled for some time and my responses will reflect my situation. Also, do not worry, I do not consider the survey I did today to be gambling, so do not be concerned about having triggered me back into gambling.
